/* Table: "CON_ConSignedRental" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_ConSignedRental"
(
"SignedRentalID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SignedMgmtID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"SignedRentaNum" INTEGER not null,
"SignedRentalName" VARCHAR2(100) not null,
"RegisteredAddress" VARCHAR2(500) not null,
"LegalPerson" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"AccountName" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"OpenAccountName" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"OpenAccoun" VARCHAR2(200) not null,
"ContactName" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"ContactAddress" NVARCHAR2(200) not null,
"ContactTel" NVARCHAR2(50) not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
constraint PK_CON_CONSIGNEDRENTAL primary key ("SignedRentalID")
);
